### Arabic

وَهَـٰذَا صِرَٰطُ رَبِّكَ مُسْتَقِيمًا ۗ قَدْ فَصَّلْنَا ٱلْـَٔايَـٰتِ لِقَوْمٍ يَذَّكَّرُونَ

### English

That is your Lord’s Path—perfectly straight. We have already made the signs clear to those who are mindful.